text: Rolf Strandberg (4 August 1937 - 15 July 2011) was a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1937 births Category:2011 deaths Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:People from Örnsköldsvik Municipality
